# 🛡️ Custom Firewall Script

This project is a simple Linux-based custom firewall implemented using `iptables`.  
It allows users to manage network traffic, block ports, and log unauthorized connections.

## 🔧 Features
- Block/Allow specific IPs or ports
- Drop incoming/outgoing packets
- Basic logging of denied connections
- Easy to extend for network defense labs

## 🚀 Usage
```bash
sudo bash custom_firewall.sh




